// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1802 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9342ed03-54bb-52d0-84b5-0a29ed88bb24

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
